{"tid":1456220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致機場迷惘的手足","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:25.000Z","uid":15971,"like":90,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ac0e13b6a6e32ca94373ee773671ade3f8fbf370","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:51:50.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">想留守嘅：</span></strong><br />\n雖然機場日日都有人送機接機<br />\n但因為大家行為、理念相同<br />\npopo已經有足夠理據<br />\n控告留守嘅人 非法集結<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">決定留就要做好準備受傷或被捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>想離開嘅：</strong></span><br />\n現時巴士同的士都唔入T1同T2<br />\n離開只能用機鐵（塞到pk）<br />\n現場有唔少人步行往東涌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>個人感想：</strong><br />\n大家今日成功癱瘓香港航空交通<br />\n如果之後想再嚟 可以參考popo扮示威者<br />\n日日着唔同色嘅衫入機場扮接機<br />\n警察吹你唔漲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">時代革命<br />\n光復香港</span></span>"},{"pid":"5b26a7829bb9f4be9998ec72e682d7d3b9185c03","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"93244b80f2c00a8c39a300005647c6159d31a4c3","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:52:57.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"4868690edb11ded0f3cc3e1c114fd3432f8daa1f","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q&d=nSJvRvahoV7vX7tkwZxFzkoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=29dd17fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAFNUI_O50xAjk_0N0Q</a>"},{"pid":"77d89e998f3d601f2b2b99e6e29183b5ca4f4c0d","tid":1456220,"uid":123898,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">機場係孤島，平時可以自己決定走定唔走，但佢一封交通就等死</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今日達到目標咗架喇，唔走等比啲鬼伏你?</span>"},{"pid":"174187854cfd792d98aedc24fa56eec2397214d6","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:24.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"5dddf158de8b495e2797813283bea374c4fda196","tid":1456220,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"1. 我哋目的係向外宣傳，冇機冇旅客，等於冇宣傳<br />\n<br />\n2. 我哋目的可能係癱瘓機場，依家所有班機都取消，已經癱瘓咗機場<br />\n<br />\n留低有咩做？？自己問下自己。<br />\n<br />\n到時機場回復運作咪再入過囉，更加唔好講夜晚收工接力的手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814fc98f5b137fc96b34afac34b82c7e53ed7608","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:34.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"0545f77dab79493b9dafd7b5a3faf0082826566a","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:53:46.000Z","msg":"<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"9681dc31ad0232696a8e57f3565a6472bb322dc2","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:18.000Z","msg":"希望大家廣傳 大家加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67c09c1f72fe64e467ae9ccee63daeebe39a9bb","tid":1456220,"uid":15971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:54:35.000Z","msg":"推上去<br />\n<code>我無野講 我唔解鎖 我搵律師 唔好凶我</code>"},{"pid":"e7d1818d9c3fbc7da95fb4293f2d539c6e9a2c5c","tid":1456220,"uid":233534,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,